The Concept is Same by Creating Outbox Table. 
But here CDC Can be used to monitor the outbox table for new Records, Extracts the Data Changes that propergated to the Target Microservices.
Using CDC, with outbox pattern allows microservices to decouple their data updates from process of propergating those updates to microservices.


Database Used for CDC:

1. Cockroach DB
2. Dynamo DB
